Effect of Pt film thickness on HER enhancement. (a) Onset potential of the HER and (b) cathodic current as functions of applied bias voltage measured on the Pt/Si nanodiode electrodes with varied Pt film thickness. (c) Response of the cathodic current when applying a forward bias voltage to the Pt/Si nanodiode electrode. The measurement of cathodic current for (b,c) is performed at the potential of the working electrode E = −0.1 (V vs RHE). All measurements were carried out in 0.5 M H2SO4. (d) SEM images of the cleaved cross-sections of the Pt/Si contacts.

